---
import Social from './Social.astro';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-slate-900">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About Me</h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-purple-600 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Benjamin loves puzzles, making connections between seemingly unrelated things, and machines that do their jobs very well. Whether it be coding, producing music, or writing, he loves tinkering and recreating beautiful things to see how they work— to add more beauty to the world.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mt-6">
        Currently he is a Cloud DevOps Engineer with the U.S. Department of the Interior, specializing in AWS infrastructure, automation, and CI/CD pipelines. When not building cloud solutions, you'll find him producing electronic music, writing, or expirementing with visual media.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 mt-16">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">AWS</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Cloud Platform</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">Python</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Automation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">GitLab</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">CI/CD</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">IaC</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Infrastructure</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">Ansible</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Config Mgmt</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-12">
      <Social name="github" href="https://github.com/VoxideNebula" />
      <Social name="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/@benjaminbushnell" />
      <Social name="bluesky" href="https://bsky.app/profile/benjaminbushnell.com" />
      <Social name="linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/benjamin-bushnell-aa8478169/" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
